.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
2 different pets are kept: snake, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Pet     | chinchilla | snake |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, pumpkin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower
1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |
| Food        | pumpkin | blueberry  |
| Sport       | surfing | volleyball |
| Flower   | tulip    | sunflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-9::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, swisher
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, scientist
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, r&b
1. the scientist is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Cigar         | swisher | bolivar    |
| Job           | bartender   | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | classical |

